import React from 'react'


const CreateSVG = (props) => {
    const maskGradient = 'create_gradient-' + props.id
    const maskCharacter = 'create_character-' + props.id

    return (
        <svg width="100%" height="100%" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 282.22 282.22">
            <defs>
                <clipPath id={maskGradient}>
                    <circle cx="139.81" cy="138.41" r="107.24" fill="#eb25d2" stroke-width=".34592"/>
                </clipPath>
                <clipPath
                    id={maskCharacter}>
                    <path
                        d="m180.03 0.011271h-91.349v45.369c-33.651 18.64-56.432 54.511-56.432 95.702 0 60.382 48.952 109.33 109.34 109.33 60.385 0 109.34-48.949 109.34-109.33 0-46.853-29.473-86.823-70.892-102.38z"
                        stroke-width=".35269"/>
                </clipPath>
            </defs>
            <image transform="matrix(1.0204 0 0 1.0204 -1.1926 -.10558)" x="-.0011139" y="-.0011139" width="282.22"
                   height="282.22" clip-path="url(#create-b)" preserveAspectRatio="none"
                   clipPath={`url(#${maskGradient})`}
                   href={props.img_src_create_gradient} className='gradient'/>
            <image x="-.0011139" y="-.0011139" width="282.22" height="282.22" preserveAspectRatio="none"
                   href={props.img_src_shadow}/>
            <image x="-.02335" y="1.0413" width="282.22" height="282.22" clip-path="url(#create-a)"
                   preserveAspectRatio="none"
                   clipPath={`url(#${maskCharacter})`} href={props.img_src_create_character} className='character'/>
        </svg>


    )
}

CreateSVG.defaultProps = {
    img_src_create_character: '/playground_assets/create_character.png',
    img_src_create_gradient: '/playground_assets/create_gradient.png',
    img_src_shadow: '/playground_assets/ring_shadow.png',
}


export default CreateSVG
